<div class="spell-book chat-release">
  <div class="release-header">
    <i class="fa-solid fa-book-sparkles"></i>
    <strong>{{localize "SPELLBOOK.Release.Title" version=version}}</strong>
  </div>

  <div class="release-body">
    <p class="release-patreon">
      <strong><a href="https://www.patreon.com/3deathsaves" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><i
            class="fa-brands fa-patreon"></i> Now on Patreon!</a></strong>
    </p>

    <h4>{{localize "SPELLBOOK.Release.BugFixes"}}</h4>
    <ul>
      <li>Fixed Troubleshooter Download and Copy buttons that failed to produce a report.</li>
    </ul>

    <h4>{{localize "SPELLBOOK.Release.Changes"}}</h4>
    <ul>
      <li>Actor export now restricted to owned player characters with spellcasting classes.</li>
      <li>Troubleshooter report now lists disabled modules with counts and dumps dnd5e Compendium Browser source
        configuration to surface disabled packs.</li>
      <li>Troubleshooter window is now resizable, with scrollable actor hint and report panes.</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <a class="open-note" href="{{repoUrl}}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
    <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-up-right-from-square"></i> {{localize "SPELLBOOK.Release.ReleaseNotes"}}
  </a>
</div>
